---
title: Beef Tenderloin & Balsamic Steak Sauce with Chive Mashed Potatoes & Roasted Asparagus
description: If nothing says “date night” like a juicy steak, then this dish is the equivalent of getting down on one knee. Here, melt-in-your-mouth beef tenderloin (the same cut as filet mignon!) is seared and then drizzled with a rich balsamic pan sauce (cue the swoons). On the side, there’s crisp roasted asparagus and creamy chive-flecked mashed potatoes. No matter who you cook this for, we have a good feeling they’ll be quite smitten.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/645ba08dd75fee027303f413-88bd0dfb.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/64e4be0554b67122d59a9451.pdf
servings: 2
author: HelloFresh
cuisine: North America
course: main course
time required: 40 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 620 kcal
  fat: 33 g
  saturated fat: 15 g
  carbohydrates: 45 g
  sugar: 9 g
